egration.png?w=768&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 768w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1722863117-right_integration.png?w=1024&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1024w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1722863117-right_integration.png?w=1248&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1248w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1722863117-right_integration.png?w=1970&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1970w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1722863117-right_integration.png?w=2496&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 2496w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1722863117-right_integration.png?w=307&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 307w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1722863117-right_integration.png?w=394&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 394w" onerror="this.classList.add('uy-invisible')" fetchpriority="auto" width="746" height="1150" class="Img uy-size-full uy-object-cover"> </div> </div>  </section> </div><div data-section="FeaturesListRecord"> <section class="Section uy-max-w-screen">  <div class="FeaturesListRecord"> <div class="uy-flex uy-flex-col uy-items-center uy-gap-300"> <div class="BlockHeader uy-flex uy-max-w-[819px] uy-flex-col uy-gap-100 uy-mx-auto uy-text-center"><h2 class="title2Font uy-font-title uy-font-semibold uy-text-1000 md:uy-text-1200 uy-leading-125 uy-text-content-heading">Paie, congés, entretiens annuels ? On s’occupe de tout ! </h2><p class="uy-text-content-text">Un logiciel de paie, c’est bien. Mais pourquoi ne pas centraliser aussi vos processus administratifs et RH ? </p></div>  </div> <div class="uy-mt-600 uy-grid uy-grid-cols-12 uy-gap-250"> <div class="uy-col-span-12 md:uy-col-span-7 uy-rounded-300 uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-flex uy-w-full uy-flex-col uy-justify-between"> <div class="uy-p-400 md:uy-p-600"> <h3 class="uy-text-content-heading title3Font uy-font-title uy-font-semibold uy-text-600 md:uy-text-800 uy-leading-125">Automatisation paie et déclarations sociales</h3> <p>Absence, prime, note de frais : les variables de paie sont intégrées en temps réel sur le bulletin de paie. </p> </div> <div class="uy-aspect-spotMedium uy-w-full uy-relative uy-overflow-hidden uy-rounded-b-[28px]"> <img src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220770-state-default-4x.png" alt="Illustration d'une fiche de paie simplifiée disponible dans le logiciel de paie." sizes="(min-width: 1360px) 720px, (min-width: 780px) 53.75vw, calc(100vw - 32px)" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220770-state-default-4x.png?w=328&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 328w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220770-state-default-4x.png?w=768&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 768w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220770-state-default-4x.png?w=1024&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1024w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220770-state-default-4x.png?w=1248&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1248w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220770-state-default-4x.png?w=1970&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1970w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220770-state-default-4x.png?w=2496&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 2496w" onerror="this.classList.add('uy-invisible')" fetchpriority="auto" width="2712" height="2000" class="Img"> </div> </div><div class="uy-col-span-12 md:uy-col-span-5 uy-rounded-300 uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-flex uy-w-full uy-flex-col uy-justify-between"> <div class="uy-p-400 md:uy-p-600"> <h3 class="uy-text-content-heading title3Font uy-font-title uy-font-semibold uy-text-600 md:uy-text-800 uy-leading-125">Congés et absences</h3> <p>Permettez à vos managers de valider en direct les demandes de congés. À peine acceptées, déjà impactées sur le bulletin de paie.</p> </div> <div class="uy-aspect-spotMedium uy-w-full uy-relative uy-overflow-hidden uy-rounded-b-[28px]"> <img src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220791-status-hover-4x.png" alt="Illustration d'un planning d'employé sur lequel figure une demande de congé parental, de congés payés et de RTT en attente de validation ainsi qu'une absence médicale approuvée." sizes="(min-width: 1360px) 508px, (min-width: 780px) 38.39vw, calc(100vw - 32px)" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220791-status-hover-4x.png?w=328&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 328w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220791-status-hover-4x.png?w=768&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 768w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220791-status-hover-4x.png?w=1024&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1024w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220791-status-hover-4x.png?w=1248&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1248w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220791-status-hover-4x.png?w=1970&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1970w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220791-status-hover-4x.png?w=2496&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 2496w" onerror="this.classList.add('uy-invisible')" fetchpriority="auto" width="2016" height="2000" class="Img"> </div> </div><div class="uy-col-span-12 md:uy-col-span-5 uy-rounded-300 uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-flex uy-w-full uy-flex-col uy-justify-between"> <div class="uy-p-400 md:uy-p-600"> <h3 class="uy-text-content-heading title3Font uy-font-title uy-font-semibold uy-text-600 md:uy-text-800 uy-leading-125">Gestion du temps et des activités</h3> <p>Suivez le temps de travail de vos collaborateurs sans alourdir leur quotidien via la pointeuse digitale. </p> </div> <div class="uy-aspect-spotMedium uy-w-full uy-relative uy-overflow-hidden uy-rounded-b-[28px]"> <img src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220810-property-1-default-4x.png" alt="Illustration montrant l'application PayFit sur mobile, on y voit une pointeuse numérique." sizes="(min-width: 1360px) 508px, (min-width: 780px) 38.39vw, calc(100vw - 32px)" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220810-property-1-default-4x.png?w=328&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 328w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220810-property-1-default-4x.png?w=768&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 768w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220810-property-1-default-4x.png?w=1024&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1024w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220810-property-1-default-4x.png?w=1248&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1248w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220810-property-1-default-4x.png?w=1970&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1970w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220810-property-1-default-4x.png?w=2496&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 2496w" onerror="this.classList.add('uy-invisible')" fetchpriority="auto" width="2016" height="2000" class="Img"> </div> </div><div class="uy-col-span-12 md:uy-col-span-7 uy-rounded-300 uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-flex uy-w-full uy-flex-col uy-justify-between"> <div class="uy-p-400 md:uy-p-600"> <h3 class="uy-text-content-heading title3Font uy-font-title uy-font-semibold uy-text-600 md:uy-text-800 uy-leading-125">Gestion des arrivées</h3> <p>Fluidifiez l’arrivée de vos nouveaux talents grâce à nos modèles de contrat, à la signature électronique et à notre mémo onboarding.</p> </div> <div class="uy-aspect-spotMedium uy-w-full uy-relative uy-overflow-hidden uy-rounded-b-[28px]"> <img src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220825-state-default-4x-1.png" alt="Illustration d'un modèle de contrat de CDI, avec un rendu imagé du document a signer." sizes="(min-width: 1360px) 720px, (min-width: 780px) 53.75vw, calc(100vw - 32px)" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220825-state-default-4x-1.png?w=328&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 328w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220825-state-default-4x-1.png?w=768&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 768w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220825-state-default-4x-1.png?w=1024&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1024w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220825-state-default-4x-1.png?w=1248&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1248w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220825-state-default-4x-1.png?w=1970&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1970w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220825-state-default-4x-1.png?w=2496&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 2496w" onerror="this.classList.add('uy-invisible')" fetchpriority="auto" width="2712" height="2000" class="Img"> </div> </div><div class="uy-col-span-12 uy-rounded-300 uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-flex uy-w-full uy-flex-col uy-justify-between"> <div class="uy-p-400 md:uy-p-600"> <h3 class="uy-text-content-heading title3Font uy-font-title uy-font-semibold uy-text-600 md:uy-text-800 uy-leading-125">Performance et engagement</h3> <p>Piochez parmi nos modèles à personnaliser pour tous types d’entretiens : annuel, professionnel, individuel.</p> </div> <div class="uy-aspect-spotMedium uy-w-full uy-relative uy-overflow-hidden uy-rounded-b-[28px]"> <img src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220841-state-default-4x-2.png" alt="Illustration d'une capture d'écran du logiciel de paie et d'un mobile sur lequel on voir un questionnaire sur le ressenti au travail d'un employé." sizes="(min-width: 1360px) 1248px, calc(94.23vw - 15px)" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220841-state-default-4x-2.png?w=328&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 328w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220841-state-default-4x-2.png?w=768&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 768w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220841-state-default-4x-2.png?w=1024&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1024w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220841-state-default-4x-2.png?w=1248&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1248w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220841-state-default-4x-2.png?w=1970&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 1970w, https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1721220841-state-default-4x-2.png?w=2496&dpr=1&q=90&auto=format&fit=max 2496w" onerror="this.classList.add('uy-invisible')" fetchpriority="auto" width="4808" height="2788" class="Img"> </div> </div> </div> </div>  </section> </div><div data-section="TestimonialCarousselAutoScrollingRecord"> <section class="Section uy-max-w-screen">  <div class="TestimonialCarousselAutoSection uy-max-w-screen uy-overflow-hidden uy-flex uy-flex-col uy-gap-600 container_full"> <div class="uy-flex uy-flex-col uy-gap-200 uy-justify-center uy-items-center uy-max-w-[849px] uy-mx-auto"> <div class="uy-max-w-[135px]"> <img src="https://www.datocms-assets.com/50397/1719397542-lorier-jaune.svg" draggable="false" alt="Décoration de lauriers" loading="lazy" decoding="async" onerror="this.classList.add('uy-invisible')" fetchpriority="auto" width="135" height="70" class="Img"> </div> <div class="uy-inline-flex uy-items-center uy-justify-center uy-gap-50 uy-rounded-100 uy-border uy-transition-all tagFont uy-font-body uy-font-medium uy-text-75 uy-leading-150 uy-bg-theme-blue-lighter uy-border-theme-blue uy-text-theme-blue-darker uy-py-25 uy-px-125">Avis de nos clients</div> <h2 class="title2Font uy-font-title uy-font-semibold uy-text-1000 md:uy-text-1200 uy-leading-125 uy-text-content-heading uy-mx-200 uy-mt-400 uy-whitespace-pre-line uy-text-center md:uy-mx-auto"> Entrepreneurs,  DRH, Gestionnaires de paie : 
voici ce qu’ils préfèrent chez PayFit </h2> </div> <div> <div class="TestimonialCaroussel uy-flex uy-flex-col uy-gap-250"> <astro-island uid="hePeL" prefix="r641" component-url="/_astro/AutoScrollingReact.B9z05KJi.js" component-export="AutoScrollingReact" renderer-url="/_astro/client.6yfSuQ0T.js" props="{&quot;gap&quot;:[0,20],&quot;reverse&quot;:[0,false],&quot;className&quot;:[0,&quot;-uy-my-400 uy-py-400&quot;],&quot;disabledMobile&quot;:[0,true]}" ssr client="visible" opts="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;AutoScrollingReact&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:{&quot;rootMargin&quot;:&quot;200px&quot;}}" await-children><div class="AutoScrollingCardsReact uy-transition-opacity uy-delay-500 uy-duration-300 uy-mx-auto uy-opacity-0 -uy-my-400 uy-py-400"><div class="uy-relative uy-flex uy-w-max uy-will-change-transform uy-cursor-grab"><div class="CONTAINER_WITH_ORIGINAL uy-flex" style="gap:20px"><div class="ORIGINAL uy-flex" style="gap:20px" data-wrapper="true"><astro-slot name="item"><div> <div draggable="false" class="TestimonialCardRating cards uy-w-[400px] uy-mx-auto uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-border uy-border-grayscale-L3 uy-p-300 uy-rounded-200 uy-flex uy-flex-col uy-justify-between md:uy-h-[320px]"> <p class="bodySmallFont uy-font-body uy-text-75 md:uy-text-100 uy-leading-150 uy-whitespace-normal">L'outil permet un gain de temps considérable. La clôture des paies, les différents modules, le tableau de bord pour le rappel des tâches... tout est simple et fluide d'utilisation. Je tiens à souligner l'efficacité des équipes au paramétrage et du service clients très professionnel et réactif.</p> <div class="uy-mt-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> <div class="uy-h-[44px] uy-w-[44px] uy-p-125 uy-rounded-pill uy-border uy-border-border-card-light uy-flex uy-items-center uy-justify-between"> <img src="/icons/trustpilot-Z2aqslH.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" width="40" height="40"/> </div> <div class="uy-ml-150"> <div class="bodySmallMediumFont uy-font-body uy-font-medium uy-text-100 uy-leading-150">Avalor</div> <div class="captionFont uy-font-body uy-text-75 uy-leading-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> 5/5 <div class="Rating uy-w-fit uy-inline-grid uy-grid-cols-5" style="gap: 2.5px;" aria-hidden="true"> <span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span><span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span><span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span><span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span><span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div><div> <div draggable="false" class="TestimonialCardRating cards uy-w-[400px] uy-mx-auto uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-border uy-border-grayscale-L3 uy-p-300 uy-rounded-200 uy-flex uy-flex-col uy-justify-between md:uy-h-[320px]"> <p class="bodySmallFont uy-font-body uy-text-75 md:uy-text-100 uy-leading-150 uy-whitespace-normal">Un excellent outil RH. LEs avantages : l'expérience de consultation des bulletins de salaire : très visuel et très bien détaillé. L'interface globale de l'application web, très efficace.</p> <div class="uy-mt-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> <div class="uy-h-[44px] uy-w-[44px] uy-p-125 uy-rounded-pill uy-border uy-border-border-card-light uy-flex uy-items-center uy-justify-between"> <img src="/icons/capterra-Z1EggHv.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" width="40" height="40"/> </div> <div class="uy-ml-150"> <div class="bodySmallMediumFont uy-font-body uy-font-medium uy-text-100 uy-leading-150">Florian</div> <div class="captionFont uy-font-body uy-text-75 uy-leading-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> 4/5 <div class="Rating uy-w-fit uy-inline-grid uy-grid-cols-5" style="gap: 2.5px;" aria-hidden="true"> <span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-ove