urrentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div><div> <div draggable="false" class="TestimonialCardRating cards uy-w-[400px] uy-mx-auto uy-bg-surface-background-grayLight uy-border uy-border-grayscale-L3 uy-p-300 uy-rounded-200 uy-flex uy-flex-col uy-justify-between md:uy-h-[320px]"> <p class="bodySmallFont uy-font-body uy-text-75 md:uy-text-100 uy-leading-150 uy-whitespace-normal">Solution de paie extraordinaire, simple d'utilisation et très efficace : donc a la portée de toutes les PME ! Bravo aux équipes PayFit très professionnelles (et super sympas). Je recommande a 100 % (Je n'écris jamais d'avis mais la solution est trop excellente, donc je tenais à partager ma grande satisfaction).</p> <div class="uy-mt-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> <div class="uy-h-[44px] uy-w-[44px] uy-p-125 uy-rounded-pill uy-border uy-border-border-card-light uy-flex uy-items-center uy-justify-between"> <img src="/icons/google-2uDsia.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" width="40" height="40"/> </div> <div class="uy-ml-150"> <div class="bodySmallMediumFont uy-font-body uy-font-medium uy-text-100 uy-leading-150">Sopalor</div> <div class="captionFont uy-font-body uy-text-75 uy-leading-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> 5/5 <div class="Rating uy-w-fit uy-inline-grid uy-grid-cols-5" style="gap: 2.5px;" aria-hidden="true"> <span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span><span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use 