 rectifier les erreurs constatées. Très satisfait de l'interface et du chat . Il y a de l'humain derrière la technologie ! Nous recommandons.</p> <div class="uy-mt-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> <div class="uy-h-[44px] uy-w-[44px] uy-p-125 uy-rounded-pill uy-border uy-border-border-card-light uy-flex uy-items-center uy-justify-between"> <img src="/icons/trustpilot-Z2aqslH.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" width="40" height="40"/> </div> <div class="uy-ml-150"> <div class="bodySmallMediumFont uy-font-body uy-font-medium uy-text-100 uy-leading-150">Laurent</div> <div class="captionFont uy-font-body uy-text-75 uy-leading-150 uy-flex uy-items-center"> 5/5 <div class="Rating uy-w-fit uy-inline-grid uy-grid-cols-5" style="gap: 2.5px;" aria-hidden="true"> <span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span><span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#FFD23F;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> </span> </span><span class="uy-relative"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[2px]" style="color:#DFE6ED;width:16px;height:16px" fill="currentColor"><use href="/icons/pictos-3R4I1.svg#star" width="100%" height="100%"></use></svg> <span class="uy-absolute uy-left-0 uy-top-0 uy-overflow-hidden" style="width: 100%;"> <svg class="-uy-mx-[